  "page": "Josua Massey",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Massey\" title=\"House Massey\"><img alt=\"House Massey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/50px-House_Massey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/75px-House_Massey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/100px-House_Massey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Josua Massey<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Softspear</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Massey\" title=\"House Massey\"><img alt=\"House Massey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/50px-House_Massey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/75px-House_Massey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/100px-House_Massey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nJosua Massey</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nKing</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Aliases</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>The Softspear</li><li>Josua Softspear</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Massey\" title=\"House Massey\">House Massey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\nA son<br />A daughter</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Josua Massey</b>, also known as <b>the Softspear</b>, was the last King of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Massey\" title=\"House Massey\">House Massey</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Josua_Massey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Josua was slain by the <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Qarlton_II_Durrandon\" title=\"Qarlton II Durrandon\">Qarlton II Durrandon</a>. His daughter was taken as wife by <a href=\"/index.php/Togarion_Bar_Emmon\" title=\"Togarion Bar Emmon\">Togarion Bar Emmon</a>, while his son was installed as a puppet lord, after Togarion drove the stormlanders away from <a href=\"/index.php/Stonedance\" title=\"Stonedance\">Stonedance</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Josua_Massey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Stormlands: Andals in the Stormlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Last known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Justin_Massey_(Milk-Eye)\" title=\"Justin Massey (Milk-Eye)\">Justin Massey</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> King of <a href=\"/index.php/Stonedance\" title=\"Stonedance\">Stonedance</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Triston_Massey\" title=\"Triston Massey\">Triston Massey</a> </b><br /><small><i><b>as <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Stonedance\" title=\"Lord of Stonedance\">Lord of Stonedance</a> </b></i></small>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403094046\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.074 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.260 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 754/1000